[gd_scene load_steps=4 format=2]

; A tiny hand-authored scene used to round-trip the author kit (see docs/AUTHORING.md and the
; gate-6 check in the author-kit task). It is built on the pack's own TilesetFloor texture, paints a
; Mark:Spawn semantic layer, and carries an Anim:smoke motile so the importer emits spawn_cells AND
; a motile table. Kept in the tree on purpose: it is the regression fixture for `--scene`.

